[Verse 1]
Static hums ripple through the endless plains,
霓虹渗透落日的薄膜，
the Serpent King coils between fractured signals,
a shadow threading the architecture of the void.
将梦境织入崩裂的航线，
we drift, unmoored in the ruins of time.
尘封的回响在波浪中瓦解，
our love, an algorithmic loop,
folds endlessly across spectral horizons.

[Chorus]
蛇王，遗忘的主宰，
slipping through the fractures of the real.
He consumes rhythm,
